headline: Sherwin-Williams Completes Acquisition of BASF's Brazilian Architectural Paints Business
summary: The Sherwin-Williams Company (NYSE: SHW) has completed the acquisition of BASF's Brazilian architectural paints business ("Suvinil") following the announcement of a definitive agreement in February of this year and subsequent customary regulatory approvals.
